[src:dynamic-tree-structure/top-tree] In that case the distance could address an edge or a vertex between two edges.
[src:dynamic-tree-structure/top-tree] We could define Choose such that the edge leading to the vertex is returned in the latter case.
[src:dynamic-tree-structure/top-tree] There could be defined update increasing all edge lengths along a path by a constant.
[src:dynamic-tree-structure/top-tree] In such scenario these updates are done in constant time just in root cluster.
